Dr. Mark Schwartz
Mark H. Schwartz, MD, FACS is a board-certified plastic surgeon specializing in aesthetic and reconstructive surgery at his conveniently located practice on Manhattan’s Upper East Side. With nearly two decades of experience, at Dr. Schwartz practice in New York City he combines science with artistry to help patients achieve the results they desire, while still maintaining their natural essence. His state of the art plastic surgery office is staffed with a caring, professional team dedicated to making sure you achieve all your goals in a warm, supportive environment.
Dr. Schwartz looks forward to discussing your interest in plastic surgery and developing an individualized treatment plan, at his practice in Manhattan, New York City. Whether it is smoother skin, a more youthful appearance, reshaping of body contours, or reconstructive surgery, he strives to make positive transformations in his patient’s lives.

 


