Kinerase®
Kinerase is a line of moisturizing cosmetic products designed to improve skin texture and reduce the appearance of fine lines, wrinkles, freckles, brown spots and uneven pigmentation. Kinerase is useful for day-to-day improvement of skin texture and appearance, for treating skin disorders such as rosacea, eczema and dermatitis, and for post-procedure skin care. Products are non-comedogenic and hypoallergenic, meaning they will not clog pores or cause an allergic reaction.


NIA24® Skin Therapy
NIA24 Skin products are designed to effectively prevent and repair sun damage through a wide range of cleansers, scrubs, sunscreen and strengthening and recovery complexes. These products release Niacin (vitamin B) continuously into the skin to build natural barriers that effectively protect against sun damage. Any current signs of sun damage are significantly reversed, resulting in skin that is rejuvenated, younger and stronger than ever!
NIA24 products are ideal for any patients with early signs of aging who want to reverse these effects before they become more prominent. Patients undergoing serious skin care procedures can benefit from the strengthening powers of these products as well. This advanced line of products noticeably improves skin texture, wrinkles, sun damage and the overall appearance of the skin.


MD SolarSciences®
MD SolarSciences® is an advanced line of sunscreen products that provides broad spectrum UVA and UVB protection for patients of all ages. Products are available as a body spray, mineral gel, lotion or solid stick, and are all fragrance-free and safe for sensitive skin. When using, MD SolarSciences products dry quickly and give skin a silky feel without clogging pores so you and your family can be comfortable and well-protected while in the sun. MD SolarSciences also offers UPF 50+ protective clothing for extended sun protection for all of your needs.


Anthelios®
Produced by La Roche-Posay, Anthelios® is a protective line of mineral sunscreen products with the unique Cell-Ox Shield™, a patent-pending technology that provides outstanding UV protection and antioxidant protection to defend the skin from harmful UVA and UVB rays as well as cellular damage. A wide range of different products are available for daily use, when at the beach, for playing sports and for sensitive skin and children. These products are fast-absorbing and are considered a leader in high UVA protection. Anthelios is also an elegant moisturizer. It is a great make-up base and is easy to incorporate into a daily routine for year round sun protection.
 

bioCorneum®
BioCorneum is an incredibly advanced skin product designed  to minimize the signs of a scar.  Its  silicone-based formulation can also protect scars from further damage or  discoloration resulting from sun exposure.   BioCorneum is effective in flattening and smoothing scar tissue, improving  the cosmetic appearance of both new and older scars.
Typically applied twice a day or as directed by your  physician, BioCorneum is most successful when used consistently for several  months.  The silicone, though invisible  to the eye, acts like a shield to safeguard both the sensitive scar tissue as  well as nearby skin.  The product  provides much-needed hydration and promotes collagen formation in the  area.  BioCorneum also contains ingredients  that can relieve the redness, itchiness and discomfort caused by some scars.
 
Elta MD® Skin Care
Manufactured by Swiss-American Products, Inc., Elta® skincare products can be used to enhance and maintain the overall health and appearance of the skin, as well as to treat conditions such as psoriasis, eczema, incontinence and more. Products such as wound care dressings, moisturizers and sun blocks are specially designed to smooth, heal and protect the skin and can be used on a daily basis.
The philosophy behind these advanced products is that by incorporating medically-approved products into a daily skin regimen, patients can protect themselves against a wide range of skin conditions.
Elta also offers a line of wound therapy products to ensure a proper and speedy recovery from a variety of wounds by facilitating the skin’s natural healing process. These products help maintain a moist environment while keeping the wound clean.
 
Revision® Skincare
Revision Skincare offers the most effective products  available today to enhance the appearance of your skin.  Created to combat the signs of aging, the  entire Revision Skincare line is made from top quality, highly beneficial ingredients.  Each product was designed with a singular  purpose of improving the skin and has been rigorously tested and clinically  proven as a targeted solution.   Cleansers, toners, moisturizers, exfoliators and more work together to  help you maximize your skin’s full potential and look your best for years to  come. 
 


 

If you are interested in learning more about our Skin Care Products in New York City, call 212-737-9090 to schedule a consultation.






